      "description": "This vehicle is a dependable daily driver currently in fair condition. The exterior shows some age-related wear, including minor scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior is clean but shows noticeable wear on the driver's seat upholstery. Mechanically, it runs well, though it will likely need routine maintenance like new brake pads in the near future. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional car at an affordable price point.",
