    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been super well-loved, you\u2019ve found it! This car is in wonderful shape and drives like an absolute dream. It's been my trusty companion for a while now, and I\u2019ve made sure to keep it running smoothly. It\u2019s perfect for everything from your daily commute to those fun weekend road trips. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have!",
